Nana, my little Rosita. 🙏🏽You have given me EVERYTHING. I never once questioned what love is when I was around you, & never felt anything but happiness & joy. My childhood was nothing short of a dream because of you. From our after school fiestas & feasts to going to sea world & the bay almost every day, I couldn’t ask for more! If I could make someone feel half as loved as you always made me, I would be the happiest. For now, I am broken. When the tears stop I’ll remember every moment with you & smile. God always calls home the greatest people & I thank him for letting me borrow you. Until we meet again 🕊️ I love you. 3.2.47-6.6.23
